== '''Lee Morris''' ==
Lee Morris was a boy born in Norwich, United Kingdom on the 9th July 1973 to  Elijah Morris a 64 jeweler and Emily Balcombe,a 19 receptionist.in 1975 , his parents broke up. Then, in 1976 , his mother married Henry Windass, a 23 mail carrier and his mother changed her name to Balcombe-Windass. In 1977 He got a cat, Iris.In 1978, his father married Sophie Cockwallace , an 18 unemployed person.In 1980, when he was only 7, his father passed away from natural causes at the rip age of 71.He inherited £3.606.314.In 1982, he got glasses.1986 : he lose his cat, Iris, who died of natural causes.The next year, he started a part time job as a newspaper deliverer, to earn money for his study.in 1992, he had a girlfriend ,Rita Seaman , aged 18 and unemployed.Sadly, he had a cocaine overdose at the tender age of 24, when he tried it, without a kid.All his relationship attended his funerals.
